OL,3,CGrok: What is Elon Musk's AI chatbot
OL,4,Cand why is it so controversial?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer Sarah Lock
OL,8,FElon Musk has announced the arrival of
OL,9,FGrok 4, the latest model of his
OL,10,Fartificial intelligence chatbot, which
OL,11,Fhas been marred by controversy since
OL,12,Fits inception.
OL,14,FThe latest instalment was launched in
OL,15,Fthe same week that Grok received
OL,16,Fwidespread criticism for antisemitic
OL,17,Fcomments, posted on Musk's social
OL,18,Fmedia platform X.
OL,20,FSo what is Grok and what other
OL,21,Fcontroversies has it faced?
