OL,6,FWhat is Grok?
OL,8,FGrok is the creation of Elon Musk's
OL,9,Fartificial intelligence company, xAI,
OL,10,Fand was launched at the end of 2023.
OL,12,FWhen asked by ITV News, Grok explained
OL,13,Fthat its name was inspired Robert A.
OL,14,FHeinlein's science fiction novel
OL,15,FStranger in a Strange Land, where the
OL,16,Fterm "grok" means to deeply understand
OL,17,Fsomething.
