OL,3,CGrok: What is Elon Musk's AI chatbot
OL,4,Cand why is it so controversial?
OL,6,F"xAI chose this name to reflect my
OL,7,Fpurpose: helping users gain a profound
OL,8,Funderstanding of the universe through
OL,9,Fclear, insightful answers," Grok
OL,10,Freplied to our question.
OL,12,FUnlike traditional chatbots, that rely
OL,13,Fon pre-defined responses, Grok uses an
OL,14,FAI-powered system that allows it to
OL,15,Fproduce human-like text responses
OL,16,Fbased on the data it's been trained
OL,17,Fon, which is becoming increasingly
OL,18,Fvast.
