OL,3,CGrok: What is Elon Musk's AI chatbot
OL,4,Cand why is it so controversial?
OL,6,FWhile the chatbox can be used online
OL,7,For with an app, the Grok 3 instalment
OL,8,Fis fully integrated into X (formerly
OL,9,FTwitter), where users can ask it
OL,10,Fquestions. Grok 4 is currently a
OL,11,Fsubscription-based model which is not
OL,12,Fyet available on X.
OL,14,FGrok is unique from other chatbots in
OL,15,Fits ability to reply to posts on X
OL,16,Fwhen prompted, where it can make
OL,17,Fjokes, provide clarification or
OL,18,Fexplain the information in the
OL,19,Fcomments, using data it scans and
OL,20,Fanalyses in real-time.
