OL,3,CGrok: What is Elon Musk's AI chatbot
OL,4,Cand why is it so controversial?
OL,6,FMisinformation and bias are failures
OL,7,Fthat large language models like Grok
OL,8,Fare at risk of, due to a type of
OL,9,Fresponse called "hallucinations".
OL,11,FAI Hallucinations are inaccurate or
OL,12,Fnonsensical responses made by AI
OL,13,Fmodels, which can occur if the
OL,14,Ftraining data used is incomplete,
OL,15,Fbiased or flawed.
OL,17,FThe problem is that the AI model can
OL,18,Fpresent these inaccurate responses as
OL,19,Ffact, meaning someone may take the
OL,20,Finformation at face value.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
