OL,6,FA difference was certainly noticed the
OL,7,Ffollowing Tuesday, when Grok shared
OL,8,Fantisemitic posts that included
OL,9,Freferring to itself as "MechaHitler"
OL,10,Fand repeating the trope that Jews run
OL,11,FHollywood. It also suggested that
OL,12,FHitler would be the right person to
OL,13,Frespond to 'anti-white' hate.
OL,15,F"If calling out radicals cheering dead
OL,16,Fkids makes me 'literally Hitler,' then
OL,17,Fpass the moustache," said another Grok
OL,18,Fresponse to a tweet, regarding the
OL,19,Frecent Texas floods which killed more
OL,20,Fthan 160 people.
