OL,6,FMusk's company xAI was forced to make
OL,7,Fchanges to Grok during the US
OL,8,Felection, after it was accused of
OL,9,Fspreading misinformation.
OL,11,FAfter Joe Biden dropped out of the
OL,12,F2024 presidential race and Kamala
OL,13,FHarris appeared on the ballot, Grok
OL,14,Frelayed incorrect information about
OL,15,Fstate ballot deadlines.
OL,17,FThe bot claimed that the ballot
OL,18,Fdeadlines for the US states of
OL,19,FAlabama, Indiana, Michigan, Minnesota,
OL,20,FNew Mexico, Ohio, Pennsylvania, Texas
OL,21,Fand Washington had passed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
